Funny story: All of the characters are supposed to correspond to one person who was in the game.

00:05:03.720 --> 00:05:08.440
The nerd is supposed to look like me, Anthony is the playboy, Robert is the jock.

00:05:08.940 --> 00:05:15.260
The emo character is some guy in our group who really did go emo and dropped the class. Go figure.

00:05:16.260 --> 00:05:21.380
Overall, UNM Tactics was a lot of hard work, but I’m fairly proud of the finished product.

00:05:21.880 --> 00:05:25.160
Feel free to download it, play it, and share it.

00:05:25.660 --> 00:05:27.900
Just don’t charge money or pay for it.

00:05:28.400 --> 00:05:30.080
